<div class="site-wrapper-first">
  <%= render "shared/header" %>
  <div class="inner cover">

    <h1 class="cover-heading"><%= title(t('100_percent_transparency')) %></h1>
    <p class="lead"><%= description(t('100_percent_transparency_intro')) %></p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="site-wrapper-second">
  <div class="inner">

    <h1 class="cover-heading">What we do with your money</h1>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-large glyphicon-bullhorn steps" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <h2>1. Mobilizing people</h2>
        <p>To stop climate change we need to mobilize poeple to show politicians and companies that we need a systems change now.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-large glyphicon-globe steps" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <h2>2. Climate projects</h2>
        <p>We support high quality Gold Standard-certified climate projects to speed up the transition to a sustainable planet.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-large glyphicon-user steps" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <h2>3. Behavioral change</h2>
          <p>We can't offset our emissions and continue as normal. We educate, inspire and help individuals lower their carbon footprint.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

